\def\Cyrctr#1{\@Cyrctr{\@nameuse{c@#1}}}
\def\@Cyrctr#1{\ifcase#1\or \CYRA\or \CYRB\or\CYRV\or%
  \CYRG\else\@iCyrctr{#1}\fi}
\def\@iCyrctr#1{\ifcase#1\or\or\or\or\or \CYRD\or \CYRE\or \CYRZH\or\CYRZ\or%
  \CYRI\or \CYRISHRT\or\CYRK\else\ensuremath{\Omega}\@ctrerr\fi}
\endinput

Usage:

\renewcommand{\the<counter>}{\Cyrctr{<counter>}}

e.g. \renewcommand{\thechapter}{\Cyrctr{chapter}}
